name: A Prologue Edition: Farewell
description:
The jumping ceremony was done. Their feet were now worn with the celebration and dance. They moved on into the embrace of oneness. 
They held each other close.
Whispered words of encouragement and good wishes in each ear.
They drank wine.
Embraced and enchanted each other more.
And so on and so on.
They would be setting off once the dark and stillness of night was audible but now they consumed and allowed the vapours of the evening to consume them in return.
